Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Gridman Voice Drama: Episode 12.12
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Return of Akane
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:20.24,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,It's so cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.24,0:00:22.24,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,It {\i1}is{\i0} snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.24,0:00:23.36,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.36,0:00:27.39,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,After Shinjou disappeared, the summer weather ended really quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:31.78,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Ah, you're right. That said, I heard Hibiki-kun's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.78,0:00:34.94,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard he's fully recovered, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.94,0:00:40.01,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Seriously? Was it from that thing Gridman did at the end? The whatever-beam?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.52,0:00:41.03,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,The Fixer Beam?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.46,0:00:42.40,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, that. Surprised you remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:48.45,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know if it was just from that, but I'm just glad that Yuuta's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.63,0:00:51.18,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,So his amnesia is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:55.07,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Ah, gone. I heard they're still going to run some tests at the hospital, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:01:00.06,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Well, I heard his family would be there with him, so he should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:01.06,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Hm, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.18,0:01:06.62,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,So, I've been meaning to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:12.97,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Uh... Rikka-san, what do you think of Yuuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:14.39,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.94,0:01:19.38,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Aaaaah hah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.17,0:01:22.62,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Gridman told you about him. Didn't he? Rikka, don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:25.10,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Ah, right... heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:27.27,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Don't just give me a "right... heh."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:28.85,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Come on, Utsumi, why does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.85,0:01:30.33,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,No, now quit trying to deflect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.33,0:01:31.31,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Eeeeh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:32.02,Default,Utsumi***,0,0,0,,Well, are you not going to answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:33.49,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:34.65,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Then how do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:39.87,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,How do I feel, huh...? Hmmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:43.97,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Hmmm, wait, wait... eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.97,0:01:45.97,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Stop trying to change the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:48.17,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,No, seriously! Look! That person on the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:49.72,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,I said, stop trying to—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.16,0:01:55.90,Default,Ustumi,0,0,0,,No way... How is {\i1}she{\i0} here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:57.51,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,It's definitely her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.57,0:02:01.77,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,It's really her... Shinjou Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.41,0:02:08.25,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,She's... back? Akane's back? Let's go talk to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:09.73,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.34,0:02:14.29,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.29,0:02:15.29,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:21.34,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,How... Shinjou-san... why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:22.80,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Akane...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:26.61,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Eh? Sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.59,0:02:28.52,Default,Rikka and Utsumi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.97,0:02:33.99,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Uh... So... you're not Shinjou Akane?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.99,0:02:36.39,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,I'm... not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:38.17,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:39.99,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,It's really not you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:41.49,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,I... believe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:44.17,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! You're definitely Shinjou!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:47.94,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,You've got such silky hair, you're wearing a loose hoodie, and black tights!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:51.69,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,And this area which will go unnamed... it's ginormous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:55.40,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,This miracle of the universe can only be Shinjou Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:59.22,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're not her? You look exactly like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:00.70,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Can I please go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:04.14,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Hold on! Look, look! She even sounds just like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:03.68,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,You sound just like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:05.14,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,You have the wrong person!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:09.83,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Oh, then... can you please tell us your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:10.56,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:13.81,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Are you hitting on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:19.55,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,I'm not hitting on you! Look... you said that you're not Shinjou Akane, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:23.67,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Then what is your name? If you don't mind telling us...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:26.48,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,That's personal information...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:29.85,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Oh, jeez... she's not even gonna tell us her name...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.08,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Well, the way you asked her was honestly kinda scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:33.24,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,That's for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:35.76,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Wait, Rikka-san, why are you taking her side?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:41.24,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,I don't think that she's Akane. I mean, she looks exactly like her, but I don't think she's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.04,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:44.37,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,That's what I've been trying to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:47.07,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Gimme a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:49.88,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:51.58,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,A tokusatsu magazine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:56.27,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Uh... One sec... here. Look at this page.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:57.74,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Um... What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:04:01.01,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Look at this kaiju. What's its name? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:02.87,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Kaiju?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:09.95,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a really popular one. What's it called? Red? Red what? It's a red kaiju!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:11.89,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Heh. Looks like an ear of corn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:13.93,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,It's not an ear of corn! It's Red King!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:17.01,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,I don't know what that is! What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:21.59,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Rikka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:22.49,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:25.44,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,This person... is not Shinjou Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:27.36,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Why did you say it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:32.19,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,If she really were Shinjou Akane, she'd definitely know Red King! Especially the 3rd one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:33.30,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,I like the 3rd one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:35.16,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, so you are—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:42.57,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Um, my ex-boyfriend use to pick this song at karaoke. And I actually ended up liking it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:44.64,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,We're not talking about the J Soul Brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:46.38,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Well, you said "the 3rd!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:49.01,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,No, no... and we didn't need to know about your ex either!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:50.77,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Sorry... he was actually my 2nd ex.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:52.52,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,You're saying too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:54.08,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,You're pretty popular, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:57.42,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Eh, I'm not that popular...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:04:58.73,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,A popular person {\i1}would{\i0} say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:01.01,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Look how cute she is, it's not weird she'd have a boyfriend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:07.78,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Sure, but you can't just start talking about your exes... guys don't really appreciate that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:08.84,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:10.87,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,You don't understand guys at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:14.43,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Um, why is he talking like he's the representative of all males on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:17.53,Default,?,0,0,0,,Don't worry about him, he's always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:19.25,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Aaah! I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:21.13,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Whoa, quiet down, you scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:24.43,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,I figured it out! Yes, yes, it makes total sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:29.05,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,You're the person that Shinjou Akane is based on. I've seen this a few times before. Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:30.17,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:34.43,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,It's like, when Shinjou Akane came to this world, she copied this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:38.52,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry for taking up your time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:40.74,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Um, it's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:42.49,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:47.48,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,So you're a different person after all. You're not Shinjou Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:51.47,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,That's what I've been trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:54.00,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,So can I go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:57.86,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Yeah... sorry about all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:06:00.35,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Ah, you don't need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So are you looking for this Shinjou-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:07.18,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Well, how should I put it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:10.11,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Well, he really liked her,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.11,0:06:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and she...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,moved away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:18.04,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. That's so sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:27.58,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,That's... not true. I didn't, um... L-L-Like her. That much. To be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:33.12,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Utsumi-kun, come on. You're not in middle school anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:36.01,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,H-H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:41.32,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Hah! You're blushing so hard! That's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:42.44,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,I'm not blushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:45.26,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Oh really, huh? Are you sure you didn't like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:49.27,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,You... didn't like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:58.19,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,I... Um... Well... I did like her. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:07:02.26,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Oh wow! Your voice sounded so creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:04.26,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,You're the one who made me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:05.04,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,He's blushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:06.33,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,I'm not blushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:09.92,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Just go "I'm not blushing! I'm Red King!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:12.26,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Shut up! You think you're clever?! You're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:14.73,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Wait, wait... Did he just touch you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:16.10,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Huh? Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:17.79,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Can you please not touch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:21.21,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,I w-w-wasn't—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.19,0:07:19.62,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,We found a molester.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:21.92,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Excuse me! I've been molested!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.82,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:23.76,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Let's get outta here, he's gonna grab your boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:26.01,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:26.01,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Oh my god! That's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:28.34,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:29.23,Default,Rikka and XXX,0,0,0,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:30.08,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:36.76,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,I'm not going to do that! I'm not—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:40.53,Default,Utsumi,0,0,0,,Even though... I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.72,0:07:48.56,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,My belly hurts from laughing so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:49.73,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:52.16,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Who was that guy? Your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:54.96,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,Eh, I guess. We're in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:59.71,Default,Rikka,0,0,0,,By the way, can you tell me your name? My name's Rikka. Takarada Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:02.26,Default,XXX,0,0,0,,Rikka? My name is—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:07.69,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,Our laughter echoed over Tsutsujidai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:10.78,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,Our breath was white.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:15.03,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,The snow on our cheeks melted in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:19.87,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,We would never be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:22.25,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,No matter when...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:24.11,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,No matter where...
